// Config file
param.inc.php

// Dependencies
cronjob (v > 14)

// Install
    // Prestashop
When prestashop is installed:
- create a feature called "Month", retrieve its id in the database and set it 
    in the "param.inc.php" file (ID_FEATURE_MONTH) ;
- then add a value in that feature for each month of the year, and add it's id
    in the ARRAY_MONTH variable ;
- do it also for "Date end sale" and ID_FEATURE_DATE_END_SALE (no value to add);
- set other config in "param.inc.php" also in "./js/validate_order.js"
- create 4 categorie (festival, concert, spectacle & autre)

    // Check server
- set config in "param.inc.php"
- const ID_CATEG_FESTIVAL, ID_CATEG_CONCERT, ID_CATEG_SPECTACLE and
     ID_CATEG_AUTRE must be retrieved in the prestashop database.

